  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00263', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-102-5e22d328', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-03', NULL, 'essay', '若甲想在 A 大學附近投資興建套房，經其初步估計，總開發成本（含土地）約為
