  ('real-estate-appraiser-moex-00266', 'real-estate-appraiser', 'real-estate-appraiser-moex-102-5e22d328', 'sub-real-estate-appraiser-03', NULL, 'essay', '不動產投資的主要風險為何？若有不動產證券化基金 C 與 T，在景氣繁榮、景氣持平
